        <p><strong>The Social Security wage base projection on this page is an estimate.</strong> The SSA announces the official wage base each October. The tax rates (6.2% and 1.45%) are statutory and confirmed for 2026. For your 2025 return, use the <a href="/fica-tax-rate-2025">confirmed 2025 FICA rates</a>.</p>
